title: Educator Resource Packet: Untitled (Hôtel de la Duchesse-Anne) by Joseph Cornell
copy: A wonderful example of the many shadow boxes Joseph Cornell created in his lifetime, this box combines whimsical found objects including a wooden bird, a ball, bingo chips, stamps, and newspaper clippings. This teaching packet includes an essay, discussion questions, activity ideas, a glossary, and an image of the artwork.
